title: Star Wars Tales (001 - 024) (1999 - 2005) (Digital) (Gonk)
description:
Star Wars Tales (001 - 024) (1999 - 2005) (Digital) (Gonk) 


This series chronicles various stories from the Star Wars universe. It is based on the premise that what you are reading are actually comic versions of holo rentals found in Peeja Mobet's Holo Emporium. As the comics are supposed to be 'movie rentals' the proprietor claims that they may or may not be historically accurate.
